column5: Welcome to the beautiful Hill Country. Only 10 minutes from the Hill Country Galleria/Lakeway and 10 minutes to downtown Dripping Springs. Located on a private ranch with lots of privacy and wildlife. Perfectly situated for families, wedding guests, wine enthusiasts, and outdoor lovers to explore the nearby areas. You will have access to outdoor propane grill and fire pit. Pets are welcome but must be on a leash outside.
